		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: I Made a Pong Thing</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />From what I can tell of a document from SMSPower, the registers $7e and $7f can constantly be read for the pixel. Vertical (?) and horizontal, respectively.<br /><br />EDIT: It seems not so, if you're trying to put a trigger on the screen...looks like the ports can only be read when the trigger is actually fired, from what the games that use it depict.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


