		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I thought SMS games went into a loop constantly reading the lightgun until it registered a hit, then checked the beam counter value at that position? (better than the NES that doesn't even have a counter) In any case you should be able to read its value constantly as far as I know.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


